description.en:
Legends is a premium high quality digital collectibles brand powered by the Binance Smart Chain. 

The legends brand features a variety of exclusive and unique artwork in themed collections capturing legendary characters, celebrities, influencers and icons from the pop-culture and from the crypto space. 

The LEGEND token is native token used on the NFT farm. It's also a passive yield token that rewards holders by taxing each transaction and distributing the tax to holders and the liquidity pool.
